    "content": [
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "How to Use Leadpages: Your Step-by-Step Tutorial for Creating High-Converting Landing Pages",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l0",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/what-is-leadpages"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "If you’re looking to capture more leads and sales without wrestling with complex code, you’ve likely heard about ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leadpages",
            "marks": [
              "l0"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". It’s one of the most popular landing page builders for small and medium-sized businesses, and for good reason. This tutorial will walk you through the platform from zero to your first published, conversion-optimized page.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "*Disclosure: Some links in this post are affiliate links, meaning I may earn a commission at no extra cost to you if you make a purchase.*",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Why I Recommend Starting with Leadpages",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l1",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/why-choose-leadpages"
          },
          {
            "_key": "l2",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://try.leadpages.com/firi2q3gofdq"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leadpages truly shines in its simplicity and focus on results. Unlike platforms that try to be everything to everyone, Leadpages is laser-focused on helping you ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "capture leads and close sales",
            "marks": [
              "l1"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". The learning curve is gentle, and you can go from idea to a live, professional-looking landing page in under an hour. For businesses that need to move fast and test offers, this speed-to-market is a massive advantage. You can see for yourself with their risk-free trial: ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Try Leadpages here",
            "marks": [
              "l2"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 1: Choose Your Goal and Template",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Upon logging in, you’re greeted not by a blank canvas, but by a library of high-converting templates. Leadpages organizes them by goal: lead generation, sales, webinar registration, thank you pages, and more. This goal-first approach is genius—it means every template’s layout, copy prompts, and form placement are already optimized for that specific purpose.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "For my recent ebook launch, I selected the “Lead Magnet” category and picked a clean, mobile-responsive template. The quality here is standout; these aren't generic designs. They’re built based on proven conversion principles from thousands of campaigns.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 2: Customize with the Drag-and-Drop Builder",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "The editor is intuitive. You click on any element—text, images, buttons—to edit it. Drag-and-drop sections to rearrange the page flow. What I love is the ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "guided customization",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". As you hover over elements, you get tooltips explaining why they’re placed there (e.g., “Social proof above the fold increases trust”).",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Key things you can do:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Edit Text & Fonts:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Match your brand in seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Add Conversion Tools:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Easily drop in countdown timers, social proof widgets, or video embeds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Integrate Your Forms:",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " Connect your Leadpages form directly to your email marketing service (like ActiveCampaign or Mailchimp). The integrations are vast and straightforward.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 3: Set Up Your Lead Capture & Integrations",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "This is where Leadpages turns a pretty page into a lead-generating machine. In the left-hand panel, go to ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Integrations",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ". Here, you connect your email provider, CRM, webinar platform, or payment processor. I connected my ESP in about 30 seconds.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l3",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/leadpages-new-features"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Then, click on your form element to configure the settings: choose the specific list, tag, or sequence you want new leads to enter. The platform’s ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "native lead capture",
            "marks": [
              "l3"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " is robust, handling everything from basic contact forms to multi-step questionnaires.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 4: Implement A/B Testing (The Pro Move)",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Here’s a step most beginners skip, and it’s a huge mistake. Leadpages has ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "built-in A/B testing",
            "marks": [
              "strong"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": " that’s incredibly simple to use. Once your page is designed, you create a variant. You can change anything—the headline, button color, image, or even the entire layout.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [
          {
            "_key": "l4",
            "_type": "link",
            "href": "https://tonyciencia.com/en/posts/leadpages-tips"
          }
        ],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leadpages will automatically split traffic between the two versions and declare a winner based on conversion rate. This data-driven approach is what separates amateur marketing from growth-focused marketing. You’re not guessing what works; you’re letting your audience tell you. For a deeper dive, check out our ",
            "marks": []
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Leadpages tips & best practices",
            "marks": [
              "l4"
            ]
          },
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": ".",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "h2",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Step 5: Publish & Deploy",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Once you’re happy, hit publish. Leadpages gives you a unique subdomain (yourpage.leadpages.com), but the real power comes from using your own custom domain, which you can set up easily. You can also:",
            "marks": []
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Embed it on your WordPress site using their plugin.",
            "marks": []
          }
        ],
        "listItem": "bullet",
        "level": 1
      },
      {
        "_type": "block",
        "style": "normal",
        "markDefs": [],
        "children": [
          {
            "_type": "span",
            "text": "Link to it from social media profiles.",
            "marks": []
